    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "Exceptionally clean used car in mint condition. It starts, runs, and drives exactly as it should, with a very well-kept interior, clean exterior, and only minimal signs of prior use. This is the kind of vehicle that stands out for how nicely it has been maintained and should appeal to buyers looking for a truly turn-key, top-condition example.",
