    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and priced to move, this vehicle offers a straightforward opportunity for someone seeking affordable transportation or a practical project. It shows its age and is being advertised accordingly, but it still delivers strong value at this price point for the right buyer. A sensible option for anyone who wants to keep costs down while getting into a vehicle without overpaying.",
      "price": 3950.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for cheap wheels that can still get the job done? This car isn\u2019t a showpiece, but it\u2019s an honest budget-friendly ride with plenty of life left for the right buyer. Great as a starter car, backup commuter, or a project if you like tinkering. If you want something affordable without the big price tag, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Budget-friendly driver/project with strong old-school character. The engine fires up and runs, the transmission engages, and it has the kind of mechanical simplicity that makes it a great candidate for someone who wants an inexpensive commuter, shop car, or weekend fixer-upper. Cosmetic wear, age-related blemishes, and overall rough condition are present, but that\u2019s reflected in the price. If you want a cheap platform with usable core components and plenty of potential, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap way into a car today. Honest poor-condition driver with plenty of life for the right buyer. Priced to move fast.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of honest, road-worn presence that turns heads for all the right reasons\u2014a machine with stories in its sheet metal and plenty of life left for someone who appreciates grit, charm, and possibility. Whether you need an affordable daily with personality, a budget-friendly second vehicle, or the start of a hands-on project, this one offers a rare chance to get into something memorable without spending big. It\u2019s the sort of car for someone who sees potential where others just see age.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of potential, this vehicle offers dependable basic transportation at an approachable price. An ideal choice for a handy buyer, first-time driver, or anyone looking for an inexpensive project, it presents a straightforward opportunity to own for less. Priced to reflect its age and overall condition while still delivering solid value, this is a practical pick for someone who sees the benefit in a low-cost entry point.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels that can still get the job done? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a great budget-friendly option for someone who wants dependable basic transportation, a starter project, or a practical runaround. It\u2019s got plenty of life left for the right buyer, and at this price, it\u2019s an easy way to get on the road without spending a fortune. If you want something simple, usable, and easy on the wallet, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly project or daily-with-attitude. This car shows its age cosmetically, but it still offers dependable point-A-to-B capability with a drivetrain that feels willing and mechanically straightforward to work on. The engine pulls cleanly, the transmission engages as it should, and the chassis has the kind of honest, usable character that makes it a great platform for someone who values function over perfection. Not a showroom piece, but a practical driver with plenty of life for the right owner who wants affordable transportation with room to improve.",
      "price": 6400.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
